Interface Transportable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Box, CardboardBox, Package, Pallet, Product, Sack

    public interface Transportable
    EN Transportable interface used in transportable objects such as products and packages. The classes that implement this interface can be accessed by total weight. PT Interface transportável usada em objetos transportáveis, como produtos e pacotes. As classes que implementam esta interface podem ser acessadas por peso total.
    Author:
    guilh
